## ğŸŒŸ **STAR Approach â€“ Real-Time Task Example**  
**ğŸŸ¢ Situation:** A DevOps team needs to migrate manually created AWS EC2 instances into Terraform and configure them.  
**ğŸŸ¢ Task:** Use Terraform **import** to manage existing EC2 instances and **provisioners** to install necessary software.  
**ğŸŸ¢ Action:**  
